			<h2>Online Code Editors</h2>
			<br>
			<p>These online code editors will allow you to practice your code or even create full apps online, without having to download
				any languages, IDE's, or editors on your own computer.  I am not going to explain every one of these as they are all pretty much the same.  They are all nice because you can see your work immediatly, usually in a side screen right next to where you are writing your code.  If you don't want to install a code editor on your machine then these are all very nice options. </p>
